Comment: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,做好了
Comment: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,媽媽 快看快看
Comment: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哎呀 做得真好呢 米卡莎
