Comment: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來了
Comment: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎?
Comment: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的 跟你同年紀的女孩子
Comment: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這附近沒有小孩子
Comment: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們要好好相處
Comment: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也要看她的態度再說了
Comment: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就是因為這樣 才一個朋友都交不到
Comment: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪 不在家嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼先生
Comment: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是葉卡
Comment: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不好意思
Comment: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒救了
Comment: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 在這附近有看到小女孩嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有看到米卡莎嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有
Comment: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎
Comment: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸去把憲兵團叫來 要求搜索
Comment: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在山麓那等著
Comment: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,知道了嗎? 艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她真的可以賣出去嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,特地把她的爸媽殺了 還把她抓來
Comment: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你仔細看看她的臉
