Comment: 0,0:12:55.73,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而她是從前從「東洋」逃進來城牆內的最後末裔啊
Comment: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把她帶到王都的地下黑市
Comment: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓那些色老頭來競標
Comment: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其他東洋人都已經滅絕了
Comment: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她一定可以賣個好價錢
Comment: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她的父親可不像是東洋人
Comment: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她不是純種
Comment: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對啊
Comment: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真正有價值的是媽媽
Comment: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都是因為你害怕而出手殺了她
Comment: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是沒辦法的啊
Comment: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰叫她反抗
Comment: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想說的只有這些嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,葉卡醫生 我們等你很久...
Comment: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不好意思打擾囉
Comment: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我安份一點
Comment: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不想腦袋被這個劈成兩半的話
Comment: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個女人
Comment: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快逃
Comment: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,媽媽
Comment: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎 快點
Comment: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個...
