Comment: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把小孩給我抓走
Comment: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 妳最好給我安份點
Comment: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然 就會這樣...
