Comment: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝 叔叔
Comment: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經知道了
Comment: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去死吧
Comment: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人渣
Comment: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不會吧
