Comment: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是艾連
Comment: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是醫生葉卡的兒子
Comment: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳之前應該有見過我爸
