Comment: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是你嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我宰了你 宰了你
Comment: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快戰鬥...
Comment: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快戰鬥啊!
Comment: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不戰...
Comment: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就只有死...
Comment: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,贏了話...
