Comment: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這個死小孩到底在說些什麼!
Comment: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不戰鬥的話...
Comment: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就打不贏!
