Comment: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個世界
Comment: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是殘酷的
Comment: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這瞬間 我身體的顫抖停止了
Comment: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從那時開始
Comment: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經可以完全控制自己
Comment: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得我自己什麼都辦得到
Comment: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,戰鬥!
Comment: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要戰鬥!!
Comment: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從背後朝著心臟直接刺進去
Comment: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是那兩個小孩幹的嗎?
