Comment: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們只是剛好和人長得一樣的野獸
Comment: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算這時候憲兵團的人趕到
Comment: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們也早就離開了
Comment: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本趕不上
Comment: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是這樣好了
Comment: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只是你運氣好罷了 艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我責罵的是你太不重視自己的性命了
Comment: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是想快點救出她
Comment: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還記得我嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳還小的時候 見過幾次
Comment: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,葉卡醫生
Comment: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以後該往哪裡才能夠回家?
Comment: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好冷...
Comment: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經...
Comment: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有可以回去的地方了
Comment: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給妳
Comment: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很溫暖吧?
Comment: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好溫暖
Comment: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來我們的家裡一起生活吧
Comment: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生了這麼多傷心的事情
Comment: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳需要足夠的休息
Comment: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點走吧
Comment: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回到我們的家
Comment: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回去...
Comment: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有勝利的人才能夠存活的
Comment: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,殘酷世界
Comment: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該撤退了! 阿卡曼
Comment: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要爬上城牆了
Comment: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我去支援前衛的撤退
Comment: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 阿卡曼!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是對我而言
Comment: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這個世界還有我要回去的地方
Comment: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有你在
Comment: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就無所不能
Comment: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「對我而言 還有要回去的地方」
Comment: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結束護衛任務後
Comment: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,著急的趕去艾連身旁的米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等待著她的是...
Comment: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「艾連的死訊」
