Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 怎麼了 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你回神了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有受傷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你那一班呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}班...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂喂! 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼只有你一個人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且總覺得你身上黏黏的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底發生了什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我這個廢物去死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.45,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 冷靜點阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:15.76,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}夠了吧 柯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全滅了啦 除了這傢伙以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏可什麼都還沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看看周圍就能知道了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們可沒時間繼續管這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會只有阿爾敏沒事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定被當做是屍體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然遇上多名巨人讓人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過竟然只有這個爛學生存活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他們一定死不瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要我讓妳永遠無法再說話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家情緒都不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟突然間大家的朋友們都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真不愧是我的克里斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等這場戰役結束後我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}的確...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們比之前更加囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之我們不能維持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還站得起來嗎? 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉... 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去跟後衛會合...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂... 阿爾敏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走囉 柯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們奉命要繼續前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是變成了地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是之前都搞錯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打從一開始這個世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是地獄...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再也簡單了解不過的世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}試圖在這個世界中...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓自己變得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}進而拯救了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}軟弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這點讓我無法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對他們倆而言...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是要被保護的存在...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想和他們兩個一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能夠肩並肩地...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一起活在...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界上...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但如今結果卻是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}害得艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏你幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲沒有呼吸了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從剛才就對他...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做了好幾次好幾次的心肺復甦術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲他...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢娜 這裡太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點去屋頂...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.34,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不能丟下法蘭茲不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是這樣的漢娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要再試了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼做...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼做都...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 我說你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道沒有搞懂現在是什麼情況嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是知道 才會變成這樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你們想要活 就給我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別鬧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.44,Default,q,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再怎麼推 也過不去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.06,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣我們不就會被巨人吃掉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在搞什麼? 士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快去制止他們啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可...可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有種就試試啊 菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是這裡商會的老大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也不想想是誰給你們這些士兵東西吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有辦法養活這裡全部的士兵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們也給我推!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這些東西是你們用一輩子也賺不到的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要願意幫忙 就有賞!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒問題的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸會用大砲把他們做掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繼續推!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不想死的傢伙就給我推!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼無視我們啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是奇行種!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想再多也沒用!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太快了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連我們精銳部隊都追不上...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們... 在幹什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來的正好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳快叫他們來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}賞不會少給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的夥伴們一直在犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為居民還沒有完成避難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只好跟巨人戰鬥並且犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是當然的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了保護居民的生命財產
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}獻出心臟不就是你們的職責嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃免錢的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好不容易在百年間有一次機會能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是在囂張什麼啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你認為為了別人而死是理所當然的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那你一定可以理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個人珍貴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可以拯救眾人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳給我試試看啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我和妳的上司是老朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些士兵的前途 我隨便都能決定的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你要屍體怎樣說話?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會長...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把台車拉出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大姊姊 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}託妳的福 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真虧妳能收拾掉它 阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我太急於一口氣擊殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而讓刀刃變鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下次我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳之前到底經歷過怎樣的經驗...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不... 沒事...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼這個時候會想起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哎呀 做得真好呢 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個刺繡是我們一族代代相傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等到米卡莎有了自己的孩子 我就教妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小孩要怎樣才會有呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿災 妳去問爸爸看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好啦 不久葉卡醫生就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳問看看醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哦 好像來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的 跟你同年紀的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為這附近沒有小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也要看她的態度再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就是因為這樣 才一個朋友都交不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪 不在家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 在這附近有看到小女孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有看到米卡莎嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸去把憲兵團叫來 要求搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在山麓那等著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}知道了嗎? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她真的可以賣出去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}特地把她的爸媽殺了 還把她抓來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你仔細看看她的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過還是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是在問是不是你的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她是「東洋人」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以前人類也有所謂的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而她是從前從「東洋」逃進來城牆內的最後末裔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把她帶到王都的地下黑市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓那些色老頭來競標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其他東洋人都已經滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她一定可以賣個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的父親可不像是東洋人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她不是純種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真正有價值的是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都是因為你害怕而出手殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰叫她反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想說的只有這些嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡醫生 我們等你很久...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思打擾囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我安份一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不想腦袋被這個劈成兩半的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡 給我適可而止點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛? 不是說了要殺的只有父親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是 這個女人她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別找藉口了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把小孩給我抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 妳最好給我安份點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然 就會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好冷...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是怎麼找到這的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個... 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...在森林裡迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看到了這間小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小孩子獨自在森林裡遊盪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}森林裡可是有可怕的大野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過你不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要跟叔叔一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}像你們這種人就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會這樣是活該!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要再給我站起來了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是米卡莎對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是醫生葉卡的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳之前應該有見過我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我陪我爸出診來到妳家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結果...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該有三個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你幹的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你幹的嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我宰了你 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不戰...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只有死...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}贏了話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就能活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個死小孩到底在說些什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不戰鬥的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就打不贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我辦不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個景象我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}見過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論何時都在我的眼中呈現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我卻當作沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這瞬間 我身體的顫抖停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從那時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經可以完全控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得我自己什麼都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要戰鬥!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從背後朝著心臟直接刺進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是那兩個小孩幹的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是叫你在山麓等我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你知道你自己做了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我殺了有害的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們只是剛好和人長得一樣的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算這時候憲兵團的人趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們也早就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根本趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只是你運氣好罷了 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我責罵的是你太不重視自己的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只是想快點救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還記得我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳還小的時候 見過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以後該往哪裡才能夠回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好冷...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有可以回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很溫暖吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來我們的家裡一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生了這麼多傷心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳需要足夠的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回到我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回去...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有勝利的人才能夠存活的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殘酷世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該撤退了! 阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要爬上城牆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去支援前衛的撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 阿卡曼!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這個世界還有我要回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「對我而言 還有要回去的地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束護衛任務後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}著急的趕去艾連身旁的米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等待著她的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「艾連的死訊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
